Package me.efekos.simpler.items

Class CustomItem

java.lang.Object
me.efekos.simpler.items.CustomItem
public abstract class CustomItem extends Object
Template class for your custom items. Make classes that extends CustomItem to make your own custom items.

    • getId

      @NotNull public abstract @NotNull String getId()
      Returns a type id of this item. Think is as an item id like 'diamond_sword' or 'redstone_block'. This value must be different from all the other CustomItems you plan to use.
      Returns:
      Type id of this item.

    • getUniqueItemId

    • getMaterial

      @NotNull public abstract @NotNull org.bukkit.Material getMaterial()

      Returns:
      Default Material for ItemStacks about this CustomItem. Make sure that ItemMeta made inside getDefaultMeta() is valid for this material.
